profile:
Prestige Buildings 2016 Ltd is a family owned and operated business. We specialize in supply and installation of pre-engineered steel buildings, products and services in the prefabricated construction trade. Our company can facilitate projects such as storage sheds, workshops and many other residential applications. In addition, we can handle any of your commercial, industrial or agricultural building needs. 
For our customers convenience we offer additional services such as permit application, steel building instillation, site grading, concrete foundation, site supervision, general contracting, and much more.
We pride ourselves in serving the end user with competitive contracts and exceptional services. Contact us for a free quote on all your steel building projects.
